The ["UC Davis"] Religious Studies department offers both major and minor programs specializing in world and local religions. They even have a website that tells you more!

The department office is located on the 6th floor of ["Sproul Hall"] and is headed by Naomi Janowitz. Popular professors within the department include Naomi Janowitz, Whalen Lai, and ["Lincoln Hurst"].

[http://religions.ucdavis.edu/department/FrontPage]
